<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Mainz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterlassung unrechtmäßiger Zollforderungen gegen Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_529" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_529_r1l16">Den von Meıncʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_529_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ıeben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / wır haben von etlıchen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . vvıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l18">Jr / etwas neẅen ʒolles bey eẅch <expan>ʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> angelangt </del> vnterſtanden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l19">vnd etlıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch angelangt habt / Damıt wır vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l20">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beſweͣrt <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> denn Jr vnd dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l21">wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey eẅch von alter <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> bıtten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l22">wır eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſʒ ʒu beſtellen daʒ wır vnd dıe vnſern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l23">mıt <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> neẅekeıt vnd vngewönlıchen ʒöllen bey eẅch vnbeſweret </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l24">vnd bey gutem altem <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> beleıben /als wır des <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> guten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l25"><expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wol getrawen / vnd als wır dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey vns auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l26">freẅntlıch handeln vnd halten das wellen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l27">Vnd lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr freẅntlıch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_529_r1l28"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dıſem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_529" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Meincz</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan>, wir haben von etlichen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie ir etwas newen zolles bey ewch
                            <expan>zu neme<ex>n</ex></expan> unterstanden und etlich die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch angelangt habt, damit wir und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> besweͣrt
                            <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> denn ir
                        und die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey uns und wir und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey ewch von alter
                                <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn.
                            <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> bitten wir ewr
                            <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleisz zu bestellen, daz wir und
                        die unsern mit <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> newekeit und ungewönlichen
                        zöllen bey ewch unbesweret und bey gutem altem
                            <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> beleiben, als wir des
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> guten
                            <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wol getrawen und als wir die
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey uns auch frewntlich handeln und
                        halten. Das wellen etc. Und lat uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                        frewntlich <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey disem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
